      Entry: 1
      Data: "\u7236\u6A21\u5757\uFF1AES Stand / ES \u57FA\u7840\u6807\u51C6\u5C42\n\u811A\u672C\uFF1AEditorPreviewGameObjectSign.cs\n\u4E3B\u58F0\u660E\uFF1Aclass
        EditorPreviewGameObjectSign : MonoBehaviour\n\u811A\u672C\u8BF4\u660E\uFF1AMarks
        a temporary GameObject created by an editor preview. Keep this outside Editor
        folders because it is a MonoBehaviour component.\n\u6E90\u7801\u7279\u5F81\uFF1A\u666E\u901A
